Lovely Collab with Sillyveon

About me
Hiya guys >w<

I'm BZinc who lives in South Korea, and likes rhythm games a lot!
*You know, Osu, Osu mania, SDVX, O2Jam, LR2 etc*
Aaaand Also likes UMBREONS SOOOOOO MUCH!!
(You know, they are so adorable, cute and..adjlkfadljhkadsfkjladsfjklasdfkljasdflkj ;w; So PERFECT!!)

And also, I like to make new friends, so you can add me as a friend anytime too~
(Just leave a message, so I can add you later)
(and become a mutual friend~) (I won't bite owo)
(If you like furry, I will always add you as a friend >w< kekeke)

Currently, I gave up playing Mania any more, since DT is included in ranked mode.

Updated: I recently started Twitter OwO!
I might sometimes upload some of my drawings (especially with umbreons owo)


Maps I Made and I Like The Most
These are the maps I made ( with my own quality owo) and I like the most
It would be a real honor, if you play my map and leave a comment about it OwO!

1. Camellia - Fastest Crash https://osu.ppy.sh/s/481639
(First time ever with the GD OwO)
Current status: Almost done. I hope this will be ranked soon OWO!!!)

2. xi - Inixia https://osu.ppy.sh/s/496664
(Not for ranked anymore, but for a good-quality unranked map OwO! but still Work In Progress)
(Currently: Need for hitsound mod ;w;w;w;w;w;)

3. Imperial Circus Dead Decadence - Uta https://osu.ppy.sh/s/461031
(First requested map by me standard senpai Umbre ( for the easier ), and Zseikimatsu (for the harder) Thanks Everyone <3)

4. Morimori-Atsushi - Hiboshi https://osu.ppy.sh/s/491259
(First collaboration map with my best korean furry friend, [Daesu] OwO!)


Current Status


I almost play Mania every day (4k most of the time, but I also play 5~8k too owo)

And I play Standard mode sometimes (Not as often as playing mania owo;;;)

P.S. HOW TO 7k LNs ;w;

(Update: 16.08.23)
!!!BIGGEST UPDATE EVER!!!
RIP my skin
Special Thanks To [Daesu](who gave me the score number style owo)
Disclaimer
